items.title: iOS 19: All the rumored changes Apple could be bringing to its new operating system
items.description: As Apple prepares to unveil iOS 19 at WWDC 2025, several rumors have surfaced, including a potential new name for the operating system and more.

items.title: Meta reportedly in talks to invest billions of dollars in Scale AI
items.description: Meta is discussing a multi-billion dollar investment in Scale AI, according to Bloomberg. In fact, the deal value could reportedly exceed $10 billion,...

items.title: WWDC 2025: What to expect from this year’s conference
items.description: At WWDC 2025, Apple will likely focus on the next iOS, which is rumored to have the most significant design change since the introduction of iOS 7.

items.title: Axiom Space prepares for its fourth mission to the ISS
items.description: Axiom Space plans to launch its fourth mission on Tuesday, June 10 — a mission that CEO Tejpaul Bhatia described as “a little bit of a victory lap.”

items.title: Pioneering Apple engineer Bill Atkinson dies at 74
items.description: Bill Atkinson, an engineer who played a key role in the development of the Macintosh and other landmark Apple products, has died of pancreatic cancer.
